Enum Class JavaOps.JumpType

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<JavaOps.JumpType>
io.github.eutro.wasm2j.core.ops.JavaOps.JumpType
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<JavaOps.JumpType>, Constable
Enclosing class:
JavaOps
public static enum JavaOps.JumpType extends Enum<JavaOps.JumpType>
A conditional jump's type in Java bytecode. Each JavaOps.JumpType represents a condition, the jump will be taken if the condition holds.
